{"type": "article", "id": 8217, "title": "Seungji Mun 经济型椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-08T07:56:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234540tyE28L1iX5Q60qcF.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t韩国设计师 Seungji Mun 继推出呼吁“零浪费”的<a href=\"http://www.munseungji.com/#!four-brothers/c1s6c\" target=\"_blank\">“四兄弟”系列椅子</a>之后，又推出了“经济型椅子”，意在最大限度减少工业浪费。这一款椅子采用单片胶合板，只需要胶合板弯曲就可以形成椅子的形状，在大规模生产中几乎不造成浪费，同时降低了成本。椅子有三色可选，且方便堆叠。这是<a href=\"http://www.munseungji.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，可以看到他更多的作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052345370PXBp91EvCs6dt8c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234538n7IEhUSJaDkHxO16.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.48703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234538vK0kRnFXTIxQzNCH.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234539UWyicOMeTIBf8Xbh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234539fa3iPpcjQTA47X2L.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src